'''加爾各答電車''' （{{lang-en|'''Trams in Kolkata'''}}），是指[[印度|印度]][[西孟加拉邦|西孟加拉邦]]首府[[加爾各答|加爾各答]]的有軌[[電車|電車]]系統，由加爾各答電車公司（Calcutta Tramways Company，CTC）運營，是印度自1902年以來最早的電車系統<ref name="Kolkata trams to get a GenX makeover">{{cite news|title=Kolkata trams to get a GenX makeover|url=http://articles.timesofindia.indiatimes.com/2012-07-13/kolkata/32662823_1_tram-network-lrt-institute-of-urban-transport|date=Jul 13, 2012|accessdate=2015-10-25|archive-date=2013-10-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131029194058/http://articles.timesofindia.indiatimes.com/2012-07-13/kolkata/32662823_1_tram-network-lrt-institute-of-urban-transport|dead-url=no}}</ref>，也是目前印度唯一運營的電車系統<ref name=onlytram>{{Cite news|title=Reaching India|url=http://timesfoundation.indiatimes.com/articleshow/657741.cms|accessdate=27 February 2012|publisher=Times Internet Limited|location=New Delhi|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20071016221039/http://timesfoundation.indiatimes.com/articleshow/657741.cms|archivedate=2007年10月16日}}</ref>。

